title: Episode 273: Like my Outfit? (Feat. Queen Naija)
itunes:title: Episode 273: Like my Outfit? (Feat. Queen Naija)
description:
Singer, Queen Naija is here to promote her new album “misunderstood.” The ladies discuss a range of topics including raising her son in the social media era, misconceptions that the public has about her, and much more. Queen Naija not only addresses the backlash regarding people calling her a colorist, she also has something to say to those who think she can’t dress! Enjoy!
